title: 70: Lord of the Rings in New Zealand
description:
Dear Webmaster,
Please enjoy this episode of us speaking in runes about Lord of the Rings. After that, Alex gives us a much needed pick me up when he reads reviews mentioning bodega cats, who are as fuzzy as the ham they eat. So turn your ring lights on and try not to be put off to hobbits!
Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy for a monthly livestream Q&A!
Go subscribe to our YouTube channel and watch our first ever live show in New York! www.youtube.com/c/beachtoosandywatertoowet
Or check out our new merch designs in our online store at shop.spreadshirt.com/beachtoosandy.
Logo by Courtney Aventura. Theme by Mavus White.
Music by PSOVOD and tyops.
